[38;5;252mSome instructions may need to be executed before other ones, when executing all instructions. For instance, changing the packages sources or adding an installer like snap or flatpak. For that specific case, You may use the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;236m priority [0m[38;5;252m instruction, which takes an integer as an arguments. The default priority is 0, and larger value means higher priority.                                                                      [0m
[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;252mIf you use the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;236m priority [0m[38;5;252m instruction in a conditional block, it impacts the whole group (meaning you may give different priorities depending on conditions).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;252mKeep in mind that it only impacts the order of execution and display in the interface. You still can manually apply instructions of lower priority before instructions of higher priority.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             [0m
[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;252mFor instance:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;251m[0m[38;5;252m  [0m[38;5;251mFlatpak[38;5;252m [0m[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             [0m
[0m[38;5;252m  [0m[38;5;251m  priority 1[38;5;252m [0m[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        [0m
[0m[38;5;252m  [0m[38;5;251m  apt.install flatpak[38;5;252m [0m[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               [0m
