[38;5;252mIn order to keep the configuration simple, some common groups may be defined in cookbooks, available locally on your filesystem or online.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             [0m
[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;252mThe [0m[38;5;203;48;5;236m cookbook [0m[38;5;252m instruction, used at the root level of your configuration file (the same place where you usually put groups names), allows defining custom local files or HTTP/HTTPs URLS where to read recipes.                                                                                                                                                                                                                        [0m
[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;252mFor instance:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;251m[0m[38;5;252m  [0m[38;5;251mcookbook <confdir>/myrecipes.qconf[38;5;252m [0m[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  [0m
[0m[38;5;252m[38;5;252m [0m[38;5;252m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      [0m
